{"tid":1352062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）要人！要人！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:54:29.000Z","uid":104507,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cd99d266bc736df9f028befd337394c58fc1ea3a","tid":1352062,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:19:56.000Z","msg":"依家港共就係要散播白色恐怖<br />\n要你地唔敢出嚟<br />\n如果我地727唔敢出去面對<br />\n即係我地默認屈服咗係港共令人恐懼嘅手段同強權之下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以我地727一定要出<br />\n仲要好多好多人出<br />\n到時一人一啖口水都浸撚死佢地<br />\n我地連full gear嘅有牌有槍爛仔都唔驚<br />\n冇gear嘅爛仔洗乜驚？<br />\n我地唔係出去還拖<br />\n我地係去光復 佢不出手我不出手<br />\n除非佢一出手 我地就因為自衛而往死裡地打</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">因為721元朗恐怖襲擊一役<br />\n我地又拎返世界各地報章嘅關注<br />\n727將會有各大報章 世界記者同我地同行<br />\n我地更加要向全世界揭露警黑合作嘅醜惡<br />\n港共嘅低莊管治打壓手法<br />\n唔可以放過依個機會 <br />\n將警黑同軍政府發揚光大 有咁大煲咁大</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXFNMeP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXFNMeP.png&h=1af13bed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c9MJjzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9MJjzQ.png&h=f89c282c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTQxXmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTQxXmw.png&h=add4b02e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4SUZCmx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4SUZCmx.png&h=b7c4d41f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5F2z8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5F2z8c.png&h=bccaa51c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f43169b028175186578aafb9526476f64069ecd","tid":1352062,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:20:40.000Z","msg":"727一定要出！到時見！"},{"pid":"f4ae8ef0c096204f499ced9e590cb78658aefb39","tid":1352062,"uid":201095,"like":0